---
const PLATFORMS = [
  { name: 'CHZZK', proto: 'WS · 폴링' },
  { name: 'CIME', proto: 'WS · JWT' },
  { name: 'SOOP', proto: 'WS · Selenium' },
  { name: 'YOUTUBE', proto: 'HTTP polling' },
  { name: 'TOONATION', proto: 'WS · alertbox' },
];

const MODULES = [
  'URL Resolver',
  'Managed\u00A0WebSocket',
  'Token Refresher',
  'Donation Normalizer',
  'Currency Utils',
  'Reconnect Strategy',
];
---

<section class="s4j-section" id="architecture">
  <div class="s4j-shell">
    <div class="s4j-section-head">
      <div class="left">
        <div class="s4j-eyebrow">ARCHITECTURE</div>
        <h2>플랫폼별 차이를<br />추상화하는 레이어.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="right">
        <p>
          각 플랫폼은 고유의 WebSocket / 폴링 / Webhook 방식으로 동작합니다.
          stream4j는 이 차이를 흡수하고 통합 이벤트로 정규화합니다.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="s4j-arch">
      <div class="s4j-arch-grid">
        <div class="s4j-arch-platforms">
          {
            PLATFORMS.map((p) => (
              <div class="s4j-arch-pf">
                <span class="name">{p.name}</span>
                <span class="proto">{p.proto}</span>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
        <div class="s4j-arch-pipes">
          <div class="pipe"></div>
          <div class="pipe"></div>
          <div class="pipe"></div>
          <div class="pipe"></div>
          <div class="pipe"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="s4j-arch-core">
          <div class="core-label">Core<br />Layer</div>
          <div class="core-modules">
            {MODULES.map((m) => <span class="core-mod">{m}</span>)}
          </div>
          <div class="core-label" style="text-align: right;">v1.0.1<br />MIT</div>
        </div>
        <div class="s4j-arch-pipes" style="height: 40px;">
          <div></div>
          <div class="pipe"></div>
          <div></div>
          <div class="pipe"></div>
          <div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="s4j-arch-out">
          <div class="s4j-arch-out-card">
            <span class="name">onChat(platform, channelId, nickname, message)</span>
            <span class="desc"
              >통합 채팅 이벤트 — 어떤 플랫폼에서 왔든 동일한 시그니처</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="s4j-arch-out-card">
            <span class="name">onDonation(Donation donation)</span>
            <span class="desc"
              >type · status · amountInKRW · formattedAmount 포함된 단일 record</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
